 provide as much details as possible so that we can solve your problem faster. We recommend you to send us a screenshot(s) with issues explained and your website\'s address (URL).'=>'When you submit the support ticket, please try to provide as much details as possible so that we can solve your problem faster. We recommend you to send us a screenshot(s) with issues explained and your website\'s address (URL).','Before you send us a support ticket for any issues, please make sure you have updated the theme to the latest version. We might have fixed the bug in the theme update.'=>'Before you send us a support ticket for any issues, please make sure you have updated the theme to the latest version. We might have fixed the bug in the theme update.','How can I solve my issues quickly and get faster support?'=>'How can I solve my issues quickly and get faster support?','If this didn\'t help, please %1$scontact us%2$s.'=>'If this didn\'t help, please %1$scontact us%2$s.','Why is my theme not working well?'=>'Why is my theme not working well?','How do I change the copyright text?'=>'How do I change the copyright text?','The Pro version is built with lots of flexibility in mind for future upgrades. Therefore, it is slightly different than the free theme but extremely flexible and easy-to-use.'=>'The Pro version is built with lots of flexibility in mind for future upgrades. Therefore, it is slightly different than the free theme but extremely flexible and easy-to-use.','When you upgrade to the Pro theme, your posts, pages, media, categories, and other data will remain intact-- all your data is saved.'=>'When you upgrade to the Pro theme, your posts, pages, media, categories, and other data will remain intact-- all your data is saved.','Upgrading to the Pro version- will I lose my changes?'=>'Upgrading to the Pro version- will I lose my changes?','With Premium version, besides the extra features and frequent updates, you get premium support. If you run into any theme issues, you will get a lot quicker response compared to the free support.'=>'With Premium version, besides the extra features and frequent updates, you get premium support. If you run into any theme issues, you will get a lot quicker response compared to the free support.','What are the advantages of upgrading to the Premium version?'=>'What are the advantages of upgrading to the Premium version?','To solve the issue, deactivate all the plugins first, except the ones recommended by the theme. Then, hard reload your website using %1$s"Ctrl+Shift+R"%2$s on Windows and %1$s"Cmd+Shift+R"%2$s on Mac. If the issues are fixed, start activating the plugins one by one, and reload and check your site each time. This will help you find out the plugin that is causing the problem.'=>'To solve the issue, deactivate all the plugins first, except the ones recommended by the theme. Then, hard reload your website using %1$s"Ctrl+Shift+R"%2$s on Windows and %1$s"Cmd+Shift+R"%2$s on Mac. If the issues are fixed, start activating the plugins one by one, and reload and check your site each time. This will help you find out the plugin that is causing the problem.','Overall, you will have more control over your website with the Pro version. You can find out more about the difference between Free and Pro versions 
